snippet.title: Tazkabaz
snippet.description:
★❤★

Hello and welcome to my YouTube channel!

I make Sims videos, as well as documenting stream highlights and memories! I stream every weekday on my Twitch channel!

Subscribe and hit that notification button if you'd like to see what I get up to!

Thank you x
